\left(\sum_{n=0}^\infty a_n\right)\left(\sum_{i=0}^\infty b_i\right) = \lim_{n\to\infty}\sum_{i=0}^n a_i \cdot\lim_{n \to \infty } \sum_{i=0}^n b_i = \lim_{n \to \infty } \sum_{i=0}^n a_i \sum_{i=0}^n b_i 
= \lim_{n \to \infty } \sum_{i=0}^n \sum_{j=0}^ia_jb_{i-j} = \sum_{i=0}^\infty \sum_{j=0}^ia_jb_{i-j}
\left(\sum_{i=0}^n a_i\right)\left(\sum_{i=0}^nb_i\right) = \sum_{i=0}^n \sum_{j=0}^i a_jb_{i-j}
